OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a mostly cloudy day
OL,6,Fwith some patchy light rain or
OL,7,Fdrizzle, mainly in the afternoon.
OL,8,FDrier at first with a little
OL,9,Fbrightness.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy through the
OL,12,Fevening with some patchy light rain.
OL,13,FThis clearing northeast overnight to
OL,14,Fbecome dry for a time. Cloud and some
OL,15,Frain arrive from the west by morning.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FA dry start in the east with
OL,18,Fsome brightness. Cloud and outbreaks
OL,19,Fof rain soon spread east, heavy for a
OL,20,Ftime. This clearing east through the
OL,21,Fevening. Occasionally breezy winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
